      <span class="section-label">Quick Start</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Simple, powerful, familiar</h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        Write real-time applications with clean, annotation-based Java on the server
        and intuitive JavaScript on the client.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="code-panels">
      <div class="code-panel">
        <div class="code-header">
          <div class="code-dots">
            <span></span>
